3 Themes for red-green or blue-yellow color deficiency
******************************************************

Most items in the ‘ef-themes’ collection are designed to use colors from
many parts of the spectrum.  Those items generally are inappropriate for
users with red-green or blue-yellow color deficiency (deuteranopia and
tritanopia, respectively).  We do, nonetheless, provide light and dark
themes that are optimized for such cases.  The names of the themes are:

   • ‘ef-deuteranopia-dark’ and ‘ef-deuteranopia-light’ for red-green
     color deficiency;
   • ‘ef-tritanopia-dark’ and ‘ef-tritanopia-light’ for blue-yellow
     color deficiency;

   *note Loading a theme::.


